@* 果醬罐 logo + OPEN JAM 字標（hover 罐蓋彈開 / 粉色果醬塗抹，動畫在 site.css .oj-logo）。
   文字顏色由容器決定：.brand-panel 內為白字、.mobile-brand 內為墨字。 *@
<span class="brand-lockup oj-logo">
    @IconHelper.BrandJar(40)
    <span class="brand-word">
        <span>OPEN</span>
        <span class="brand-jam">
            @IconHelper.JamSmear()
            <span class="brand-jam-text">JAM</span>
        </span>
    </span>
</span>
